{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"popstate","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>O evento&nbsp;<code>popstate </code>é disparado quando a entrada do&nbsp;histórico&nbsp;ativa é alterado. Se o histórico de entrada a ser ativado for criado por uma chamada&nbsp;<code>history.pushState()&nbsp;</code>ou for afetada por uma&nbsp;chamada&nbsp;<code>history.replaceState(),</code>&nbsp;a&nbsp;propriedade&nbsp;dos eventos<code> popstate </code>contém uma cópia do histórico de entrada do objeto.<br>\n <br>\n Note &nbsp;que apenas chamando&nbsp;<code>history.pushState()</code> ou&nbsp;<code>history.replaceState()</code>&nbsp;não ira disparar um evento&nbsp;<code>popstate.&nbsp;</code>O evento <code>popstate </code>apenas é disparado após uma ação no navegador como um click no botão de voltar (ou chamando <code>history.back() por javascript</code>)<br>\n <br>\n Navegadores tendem a lidar com o evento <code>popstate&nbsp;</code>diferentemente no carregamento da página.&nbsp;Chrome (anterior versão 34) e&nbsp;Safari sempre emitem um evento <code>popstate</code> no carregamento da página, mas o Firefox&nbsp;não.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"informação_geral","title":"Informação&nbsp;geral","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"especificação\">Especificação</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/history.html#event-popstate\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">PopStateEvent</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Yes</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"alvo\">Alvo</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">defaultView</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"ação_padrão\">Ação padrão</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">None</dd>\n</dl>","titleAsText":"Informação geral"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The browsing context (<code>window</code>).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>state</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td><em>any</em></td>\n   <td>The current history entry's state object (if any).</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatiblidade_com_navegadores","title":"Compatiblidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span>[1]</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>3.0[2]</td>\n   <td>4.0 (2)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span>[1]</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] A implementação tem um suporte limitado.</p>\n\n<p>[2] A implementação em Android 2.2 e 2.3 tem problemas.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Um página no&nbsp;<code>http://example.com/example.html roda o código abaixo e irá gerar os logs indicados</code></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onpopstate</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"location: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>location <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\", state: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token constant\">JSON</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stringify</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pushState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">page</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"title 1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"?page=1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pushState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">page</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"title 2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"?page=2\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">replaceState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">page</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"title 3\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"?page=3\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">back</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Logs \"location: http://example.com/example.html?page=1, state: {\"page\":1}\"</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">back</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Logs \"location: http://example.com/example.html, state: null</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">go</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// Logs \"location: http://example.com/example.html?page=3, state: {\"page\":3}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Observe que mesmo que a entrada do histórico inicial(para&nbsp;<code>http://example.com/example.html</code>) não tem nenhum&nbsp;estado associado a ele, um evento <code>popstate </code>é ainda disparado quando nós&nbsp;ativamos essa entrada após a segunda chamada para<code> history.back ().</code><br>\n &nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eventos_relacionados","title":"Eventos relacionados","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event\"><code>hashchange</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Informação&nbsp;geral","id":"informação_geral"},{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Compatiblidade com navegadores","id":"compatiblidade_com_navegadores"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Eventos relacionados","id":"eventos_relacionados"}],"summary":"O evento popstate é disparado quando a entrada do histórico ativa é alterado. Se o histórico de entrada a ser ativado for criado por uma chamada history.pushState() ou for afetada por uma chamada history.replaceState(), a propriedade dos eventos popstate contém uma cópia do histórico de entrada do objeto.\n \n Note  que apenas chamando history.pushState() ou history.replaceState() não ira disparar um evento popstate. O evento popstate apenas é disparado após uma ação no navegador como um click no botão de voltar (ou chamando history.back() por javascript)\n \n Navegadores tendem a lidar com o evento popstate diferentemente no carregamento da página. Chrome (anterior versão 34) e Safari sempre emitem um evento popstate no carregamento da página, mas o Firefox não.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onpopstate","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Window: popstate event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onpopstate","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"popstate","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window: popstate イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"popstate","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"popstate","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onpopstate","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"window.onpopstate","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/window/popstate_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/window/popstate_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event","title":"popstate"}],"pageTitle":"popstate - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}